narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Through this course I had the opportunity to receive the most attentive feedback on my writing that I have received thus far at Yale. In addition, the course's use of Yale's manuscript collections allowed me to improve my research skills.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The only weakness of this course is that it won't be offered again!

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: The model for learning in which students have the opportunity to read their papers aloud for feedback every other week is a fantastic learning opportunity. More courses should be structured with built-in peer review.
